{This is a classic Notrump bidding sequence.

NORTH opens 1NT with 17 points and balanced distribution. 
SOUTH, with 9 points is not strong enough to bid game, but invites with 2NT. 
NORTH has a maximum, so she accepts the invitation.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
